name: Teebee
description: '''Torgeir Byrknes''', better known by his stage name '''Teebee''', is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] DJ and producer of [[drum and bass]]. He also runs the record label Subtitles Recordings. Teebee began DJing in 1990 and released his first record in 1996. He won the Knowledge Magazine award for ''Best International Producer'' in 2001.
